Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yayu hurriedly entered the room and took out photos from high school to check one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He realized that the other person was his old classmate, Siwoo, and felt happy to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He tried to suggest that Siwoo stay for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Siwoo said he had to go deliver another order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not wanting to waste time unnecessarily, the two just exchanged light greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,After Siwoo quickly left, Yayu returned to his room and the more he thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.40,0:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater his sense of regret grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now approaching thirty, his appearance had not changed much from his school days.
